e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"上年6月去 覺得好食 我係去到叫酒店幫我book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112f989133e5ac19108da438e0e24608cc2daf3b","tid":195761,"uid":11687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:45:52.000Z","msg":"上次四個人8點去無Book位<br />\n個侍應第一句話無位諗住走跟住佢加多句話得10點有<br />\n即刻話ok之後落去行個圈就可以返去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab82219c39790e70e6bc81d18bb6c70183cb706","tid":195761,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"舊年兩個人去夜晚walk in等一個鐘就有位"},{"pid":"3230659a9c42d3b548f01c36b9697603ef6fa9bf","tid":195761,"uid":77056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:36:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩問左個日本讀書fd 諗住叫佢幫手book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157c45b505db0f4f57cc0ce7591652c7107a8673","tid":195761,"uid":11252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"上年食過，唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b457a4e514005c43e5491c9c4c25219eb96ff8","tid":195761,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"尋晚打電話book 左5月中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13afbc1626f2dcff1527a4a59e1d790b0afe6008","tid":195761,"uid":23217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>六歌仙唔好食 因為出左名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真呢？ 真係唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzhS1sS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzhS1sS.jpg&h=1c2fc0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJb3Fde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJb3Fde.jpg&h=3e23b825&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0W93wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0W93wk.jpg&h=7353877b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H76Afu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH76Afu9.jpg&h=4dc95958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晩市8750兩小時任飲任食，我覺得好好食。<br />\n<br />\n三月尾食，電話book，接聽個英文比我想像中好"},{"pid":"da5437ca96e4d3671cb0b5b2b6abc8924dff8eb5","tid":195761,"uid":23775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六歌仙唔好食 因為出左名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未食之前都係抱住呢個心態, 去到見到好多香港人台灣人都心諗應該係行貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點左第二貴果SET, 牛係幾好食不過覺得少少油<br />\n重點係海鮮!!!蝦好大隻, 帶子又大粒! 仲有皇帝蟹腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !!我應該叫蟹腳叫到回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀佢係好出名, 但又真係值得去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.S 我係12點check in酒店叫reception幫我訂即晚, 結果要9點先有位"},{"pid":"fedd6fe577947dc09b7c28e70e47da4e02abf158","tid":195761,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪真係要book位先有得食 同埋佢海外book位果個電話打過去識唔識聽英文 驚佢唔識聽英文book唔到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇白金VISA?<br />\n可以搵白金秘書幫你BOOK<br />\n有朋友有都得可以叫你朋友用，唔使用返張卡埋單<br />\n<br />\n我覺得幾好食<br />\n款式唔算好多<br />\n基本食牛+蟹腳都夠晒"}]}